        ## Comparison Operators ##
        /*
        equal to- ==
        not equal to- !=
        less than- <
        less than or equal- <=
        greater than- >
        greater than or equal- >=

        value in collection- in
        object id match- is

        logical AND- and 
        logical OR- or
        logical NOT- not
        */

